</span></span></span></span></span><span class=3D"vlist-s">=E2=80=8B</span>=
</span><span class=3D"vlist-r"><span class=3D"vlist" style=3D"height: 0.936=
em;"><span class=3D""></span></span></span></span></span><span class=3D"mcl=
ose nulldelimiter"></span></span></span></span></span></span></div>
<p>
The area <em>A</em> of a regular polygon is equal to the number of sides <e=
m>n</em> times the length of the sides <em>a</em> squared, divided by 4 tim=
es the <a href=3D"https://www.inchcalculator.com/tangent-calculator/">tange=
nt</a> of pi times the number of sides.
</p>
<div class=3D"article-thumbnail article-thumbnail-width-80">
<img loading=3D"lazy" decoding=3D"async" src=3D"https://www.inchcalculator.=
