<h2 id=3D"idx_how_to_calculate_the_perimeter_of_a_polygon">How to Calculate=
 the Perimeter of a Polygon</h2>
<p>
The <a href=3D"https://www.inchcalculator.com/perimeter-calculator/">perime=
ter</a> of a polygon is the sum of the lengths of all its sides. You can ca=
lculate the perimeter of a regular polygon by multiplying the length of the=
 sides by the number of sides.
</p><div id=3D"AdThrive_Content_2_tablet" class=3D"adthrive-ad  adthrive-co=
ntent adthrive-content-2" style=3D"min-height: 250px;"></div>
