splay=3D"block"><semantics><mrow><mi>=CE=B1</mi><mo>=3D</mo><mfrac><mrow><m=
o stretchy=3D"false">(</mo><mi>n</mi><mo>=E2=88=92</mo><mn>2</mn><mo stretc=
