t passes through all of its vertices. You can calculate the circumradius <e=
m>R</em> using the formula:
</p>
<div class=3D"latex latex--mh6 latex--left latex--mode-display latex--bg-gr=
ey loaded" data-latex=3D"" data-latex-alignment=3D"left" data-latex-mode=3D=
